title: PAIN IS TEMPORARY #2
itunes:title: PAIN IS TEMPORARY #2
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
PAIN IS TEMPORARY! It may last for a minute, or an hour, or a day, or a year, but eventually it will subside, and something else will take it's place. If you quit, however, it will last forever. Best Motivational Speech Compilation featuring Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Dr. Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity), Cole DaSilva (https://bit.ly/ColeDaSilvaMotiversity), Bobby Maximus (https://bit.ly/BobbyMaximusMotiversity), and Mat Wilson (https://bit.ly/MattWilsonMotiversity).


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube), and Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
